   <body>
      <context>
         <note>Follow all national, local, and state codes concerning
anchoring.</note>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Drill holes in the floor to fit the 14 anchoring holes
in each of the battery cabinets.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Anchor the battery cabinet(s) to the floor. Floor anchoring
bolts are not supplied.</p>
